```cpp
// æ³¨æ„ï¼šcpp ä»£ç ç”± chatGPTğŸ¤– æ ¹æ®æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç ç¿»è¯‘ã€‚
// æœ¬ä»£ç çš„æ­£ç¡®æ€§å·²é€šè¿‡åŠ›æ‰£éªŒè¯ï¼Œå¦‚æœ‰ç–‘é—®ï¼Œå¯ä»¥å¯¹ç…§æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç æŸ¥çœ‹ã€‚

class Solution {
    unordered_map<TreeNode*, int> memo;

public:
    int rob(TreeNode* root) {
        if (root == nullptr) return 0;
        // åˆ©ç”¨å¤‡å¿˜å½•æ¶ˆé™¤é‡å å­é—®é¢˜
        if (memo.find(root) != memo.end())
            return memo[root];
        // æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹ä¸‹å®¶
        int do_it = root->val
                + (root->left == nullptr ?
                0 : rob(root->left->left) + rob(root->left->right))
                + (root->right == nullptr ?
                0 : rob(root->right->left) + rob(root->right->right));
        // ä¸æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹å®¶
        int not_do = rob(root->left) + rob(root->right);

        int res = max(do_it, not_do);
        memo[root] = res;
        return res;
    }
};
```

```python
# æ³¨æ„ï¼špython ä»£ç ç”± chatGPTğŸ¤– æ ¹æ®æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç ç¿»è¯‘ã€‚
# æœ¬ä»£ç çš„æ­£ç¡®æ€§å·²é€šè¿‡åŠ›æ‰£éªŒè¯ï¼Œå¦‚æœ‰ç–‘é—®ï¼Œå¯ä»¥å¯¹ç…§æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç æŸ¥çœ‹ã€‚

class Solution:
    def __init__(self):
        self.memo = {}

    def rob(self, root: TreeNode) -> int:
        if root is None:
            return 0
        # åˆ©ç”¨å¤‡å¿˜å½•æ¶ˆé™¤é‡å å­é—®é¢˜
        if root in self.memo:
            return self.memo[root]
        # æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹ä¸‹å®¶
        do_it = root.val + (self.rob(root.left.left) if root.left else 0) + (self.rob(root.left.right) if root.left else 0) + (self.rob(root.right.left) if root.right else 0) + (self.rob(root.right.right) if root.right else 0)
        # ä¸æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹å®¶
        not_do = self.rob(root.left) + self.rob(root.right)

        res = max(do_it, not_do)
        self.memo[root] = res
        return res
```

```java
class Solution {
    Map<TreeNode, Integer> memo = new HashMap<>();

    public int rob(TreeNode root) {
        if (root == null) return 0;
        // åˆ©ç”¨å¤‡å¿˜å½•æ¶ˆé™¤é‡å å­é—®é¢˜
        if (memo.containsKey(root))
            return memo.get(root);
        // æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹ä¸‹å®¶
        int do_it = root.val
                + (root.left == null ?
                0 : rob(root.left.left) + rob(root.left.right))
                + (root.right == null ?
                0 : rob(root.right.left) + rob(root.right.right));
        // ä¸æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹å®¶
        int not_do = rob(root.left) + rob(root.right);

        int res = Math.max(do_it, not_do);
        memo.put(root, res);
        return res;
    }
}
```

```go
// æ³¨æ„ï¼šgo ä»£ç ç”± chatGPTğŸ¤– æ ¹æ®æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç ç¿»è¯‘ã€‚
// æœ¬ä»£ç çš„æ­£ç¡®æ€§å·²é€šè¿‡åŠ›æ‰£éªŒè¯ï¼Œå¦‚æœ‰ç–‘é—®ï¼Œå¯ä»¥å¯¹ç…§æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç æŸ¥çœ‹ã€‚

func rob(root *TreeNode) int {
    memo := make(map[*TreeNode]int)
    return helper(root, memo)
}

// åˆ©ç”¨å¤‡å¿˜å½•æ¶ˆé™¤é‡å å­é—®é¢˜
func helper(root *TreeNode, memo map[*TreeNode]int) int {
    if root == nil {
        return 0
    }
    if _, ok := memo[root]; ok {
        return memo[root]
    }
    // æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹ä¸‹å®¶
    doIt := root.Val
    if root.Left != nil {
        doIt += helper(root.Left.Left, memo) + helper(root.Left.Right, memo)
    }
    if root.Right != nil {
        doIt += helper(root.Right.Left, memo) + helper(root.Right.Right, memo)
    }
    // ä¸æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹å®¶
    notDo := helper(root.Left, memo) + helper(root.Right, memo)

    res := max(doIt, notDo)
    memo[root] = res
    return res
}

func max(x, y int) int {
    if x > y {
        return x
    }
    return y
}
```

```javascript
// æ³¨æ„ï¼šjavascript ä»£ç ç”± chatGPTğŸ¤– æ ¹æ®æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç ç¿»è¯‘ã€‚
// æœ¬ä»£ç çš„æ­£ç¡®æ€§å·²é€šè¿‡åŠ›æ‰£éªŒè¯ï¼Œå¦‚æœ‰ç–‘é—®ï¼Œå¯ä»¥å¯¹ç…§æˆ‘çš„ java ä»£ç æŸ¥çœ‹ã€‚

var rob = function(root) {
    const memo = new Map();

    var dp = function(root) {
        if (root === null) return 0;
        // åˆ©ç”¨å¤‡å¿˜å½•æ¶ˆé™¤é‡å å­é—®é¢˜
        if (memo.has(root))
            return memo.get(root);
        // æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹ä¸‹å®¶
        let do_it = root.val
            + (root.left === null ?
            0 : dp(root.left.left) + dp(root.left.right))
            + (root.right === null ?
            0 : dp(root.right.left) + dp(root.right.right));
        // ä¸æŠ¢ï¼Œç„¶åå»ä¸‹å®¶
        let not_do = dp(root.left) + dp(root.right);

        let res = Math.max(do_it, not_do);
        memo.set(root, res);
        return res;
    };

    return dp(root);
};
```
